      <title>KKR 领投酒店科技公司 Lighthouse 3.7 亿美元融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/kkr-leads-hospitality-tech-firm-lighthouse-s-370-million-round</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Lighthouse 是一家帮助酒店分析市场需求和价格的初创公司，该公司在由私募股权公司 KKR &amp; Co. 领投的一轮融资中筹集了约 3.7 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/kkr-leads-hospitality-tech-firm-lighthouse-s-370-million-round</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 06:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
